"       \"Patient information: Upper endoscopy (The Basics)\"",
"      </a>",
"      and",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?10/19/10546?source=see_link\">",
"       \"Patient information: Esophageal stricture (The Basics)\"",
"      </a>",
"      )",
"     </li>",
"     <li>",
"      Beyond the Basics topics (see",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?21/0/21506?source=see_link\">",
